extendedInfo.description: What is it about the ocean that we can't have enough of it? It is the intriguing shades of blue? The calming sound of the water? This app is a simple reminder of the ocean when you are at the office, waiting in line at a grocery store or anywhere you are. This app will alternate five gorgeous ocean wallpapers with a delay of your choice. You will drift into relaxation in no time.It is very important for us to keep this app totally free with clean in-game ads.
